<LP>
   PARIS -- The state-owned French steel producer Usinor
Sacilor S.A. said it is launching a bid for 20% of the shares
outstanding of the steel trading company ASD PLC, a 77%-owned
unit of Stemcor PLC, in cooperation with the British concern.
   The French company plans a joint venture with ASD that
