<LP>
   NHI NELSON HOLDINGS INTERNATIONAL Ltd. (Beverly Hills,
Calif.) -- Peter D. Graves was named executive vice president
at this holding company's Nelson Entertainment Group unit. He
had been senior vice president.
</LP>
